        "subject": "LU-12756 lnet: Take peer NI ref in lnet_discover_peer_locked",
        "message": "LU-12756 lnet: Take peer NI ref in lnet_discover_peer_locked\n\nlnet_discover_peer_locked() requires that callers have a reference\non the lnet_peer_ni object that is being discovered. Since\nlnet_discover_peer_locked() is responsible for releasing and\nre-taking the net lock, it should also be responsible for managing\nthis reference.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Chris Horn <hornc@cray.com>\nChange-Id: I5f9db5eac77b6cdc823f727a534a08fb987032b0\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
